reviewText: First, be aware that Hawaiian Tropic helped (or at least seemed to help) produce this title, so do NOT expect to see any nude coeds. The HD quality is very good, and all of the colors jump off of the screen and and clear.  The overall topic is about the "party" during spring break in Ft. Lauderdale.  The production crew also went to Acapulco to show the viewer the "party" going on there.
